elp to attract token investors and enthusiasts.\r\n\r\nThis is why the businesses want to opt for a professional ICO marketing agency in India that is well versed with the techniques and tactics and can help in planning a result-oriented marketing strategy.\r\n\r\nWhat is ICO?\r\n\r\nExpanded as Initial Coin Offerings, ICOs are becoming increasingly popular, creating a multi-billion-dollar market.\r\n\r\nICO marketing services are being actively practiced throughout the world.\r\n\r\nThe biggest reason of ICOs gaining popularity is that the Initial Coin Offerings are giving startups in the blockchain and cryptocurrency space access to limitless crowdfunded capital.\r\n\r\nYes, the ICO revolution has begun, and they will definitely stay. Here are a few facts that illustrate the statement-\r\n\r\n– $96 million was raised via ICOs in 2016\r\n– $6 billion was raised via ICOs in 2017\r\n– $6.3 billion was raised via ICOs by April 2018\r\n\r\nICO is creating a billion-dollar market. As the Initial Coin Offerings continue to provide limitless crowdfunding capital to start-ups and entrepreneurs, it will continue to rise. But how to strategize an effective ICO marketing plan. Here are a few tips that you need to know-\r\n\r\nCraft an interesting story\r\n\r\nAccording to the best ICO marketing agency in India- an interesting and compelling story will act as magnets. Your audience wants to know your mission and those who share the same belief and values are easy to target.\r\n\r\nWhen you hire professional ICO marketing services, they will present it in a perfect way that not only attracts prospects but also converts them into supporters.\r\n\r\nKnow your audience\r\n\r\nFor all those who are in ICO marketing services know that half of the world doesn’t even know what an ICO is. So, when you plan marketing an ICO, it is best to know about your target prospects. The ICO marketing agency in India will design the plan around a particular group of people.\r\n\r\nThe professionals in ICO marketing will segment the entire marketing efforts into two- one that targets the experienced cryptocurrency crowd and other for the new. This is helpful in creating the right campaign- what all to include and what not.\r\n\r\nICO Consultant\r\n\r\nWe all know that the token market is new. And, some of the inexperienced groups are also launching coins and end up facing a failure many times.\r\n\r\nGetting in touch with the best ICO marketing agency is the right approach to enter the world. These professional companies have a team of experienced and dedicated engineers who know how to produce an amazing product and flawless code.\r\n\r\nTransparency is key\r\n\r\nThe much-needed feature of your ICO marketing plan. Even the professional ICO marketing services boast about their strategy transparency. In order to attract the interest of potential buyers, transparency is required.\r\n\r\nLack of transparency can act foul and greatly reduce the interest of the buyers. So, the best ICO marketing agency will recommend you to make things transparent, include pictures, add links to team member’s social media accounts, etc.\r\n\r\nCompliance\r\n\r\nLast but not least. ICO compliance is a very important factor. A number of issues regarding the compliance have been noticed in the past. So, when the ICO marketing agency in India will strategize a plan, they will ensure strict adherence to the guidelines.\r\n\r\nAs the competition gets tough, the regulations are even increased and there is a reduction in marketing channels, ICO marketing gets even hard. However, hiring professional ICO marketing services will help you strategize a perfect ICO (Initial Coin Offerings) marketing plan.','ICO Marketing- How to Strategize Your ICO Effectively','','publish','open','open','','ico-marketing-how-to-strategize-your-ico-effectively','','','2019-03-18 09:44:37','2019-03-18 09:44:37','',0,'http://wow.pebbled.io/schakraborty/softprodigy/1/?p=504',0,'post','',0),(505,1,'2019-03-18 09:23:04','2019-03-18 09:23:04','','post3','','inherit','open','closed','','post3','','','2019-03-18 09:23:04','2019-03-18 09:23:04','',504,'http://wow.pebbled.io/schakraborty/softprodigy/1/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/post3.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(501,1,'2019-03-18 09:19:20','2019-03-18 09:19:20','With over 4 million apps available in app stores, it can be difficult to make your app to stand out.\r\n\r\nDeveloping a well-planned and in-depth marketing campaign for your app can captivate user attention and grow your consumer base.\r\n\r\nBusinesses should launch an effective marketing strategy to increase downloads and daily active users. Use the three tips below to successfully market your app.\r\n\r\nSpread Awareness with Social Media\r\n\r\nSocial media marketing allows businesses to connect with a large audience. In 2017, 71% of internet users were also active on social media and that number is expected to continue to grow. As such, social media can help build awareness for your app even before launch.\r\n\r\nOnce your app is released, you want to immediately earn downloads, which can be difficult if no one has heard of your app. Social media provides an accessible platform for people to read your content and learn about the features and services your app offers.\r\n\r\nIf you want to capture people’s attention on social media, consider telling a compelling story or using attractive visuals to grab attention. Building suspense gradually for your app’s release will help engage people. Countdowns, giveaways, and competitions can also create a buzz.\r\n\r\nUsing social media, Starbucks ran an ad campaign asking users to submit pictures of their products. The best submissions were then shared on their official feed. When users clicked through to the Starbucks profile, the bio included a link to download their app. With this interactive approach to the ad experience, Starbucks was able to successfully drive user engagement and app downloads.\r\n\r\nSocial media allows your company to have a conversation with people and form a familiar relationship with your audience. A following of people who want to hear what you have to say is a great resource, especially when you can get your message in front of them for free.\r\n\r\nOptimize Your App Store Rank\r\n\r\nApp Store Optimization (ASO) is the process of making sure your mobile app ranks higher in app store searches. ASO is very similar to Search Engine Optimization (SEO) for websites.\r\n\r\nYour app’s keywords, downloads, ratings, and reviews affect where your app appears in searches. Mobile app development companies use ASO to rank higher in search results and on top of lists in-store, which drives downloads.\r\n\r\nAs 63% of apps are found through app store searches, you need to be sure that your app is seen in the first page of results. Using keywords in your app description and app title will help give it higher visibility in searches. The title of your app should be short, easy to remember, and explain what your app does.\r\n\r\nReviews and ratings allow users to provide direct feedback about your app and can affect ASO.\r\n\r\nAs your rating is placed next to the name of your app, it can immediately reflect positively on your user experience. People will read that others liked your app and believe in the value.\r\n\r\nAlmost all customers (97%) read reviews, which means it is essential to curate good feedback for others to see. If you receive a poor review, make sure to respond and assure them that you will try to fix the problem.\r\n\r\nResponding to user reviews can continue the conversation and further grow the user’s relationship with your brand.\r\n\r\nFine-tuning each aspect of ASO will help increase your total number of downloads.\r\n\r\nPay for Advertisements\r\n\r\nOver 50% of businesses pay for both search and social ads while almost half of clicks (41%) are given to the top 3 paid ads on the search results page. Many companies use both paid social and search ads to maximize their apps’ chances at being seen.\r\n\r\nSearch ads appear as ads at the top of search listings and next to results in the sidebar, while social media ads appear in people’s newsfeed and in the sidebar.\r\n\r\nPaid advertisements have a high success rate because you can target exactly who you are trying to reach.\r\n\r\nSocial media ads target people based on age, location, gender, device, and interest. Meanwhile, search ads appear directly in front of someone searching for a specific service. Both methods allow businesses to appeal directly to their intended audience.\r\n\r\nGoogle also offers metric tracking features when businesses pay for ads. This tracking feature shows how well an ad is performing by telling you how many people have viewed it, the number of clicks, and how many people downloaded your app.\r\n\r\nClosely tracking the success of an ad can help you adapt your marketing for the future.\r\n\r\nBoost Your App Downloads with Great App Marketing Practices\r\n\r\nUsing social media helps you to begin building your relationship with users while ASO ensures potential users can find your app when searching for it.\r\n\r\nPaid advertisements allow your business to either be the first company people see when looking for a service or to notice your product naturally as they look through their own social feeds.\r\n\r\nApp marketing can boost your app’s success and engage potential users. Hire a top mobile app developer or mobile app development company to begin your app development process.','3 Tips to Successfully Market Your App','','publish','open','open','','3-tips-to-successfully-market-your-app','','','2019-03-18 09:44:53','2019-03-18 09:44:53','',0,'http://wow.pebbled.io/schakraborty/softprodigy/1/?p=501',0,'post','',0),(502,1,'2019-03-18 09:18:56','2019-03-18 09:18:56','','post2','','inherit','open','closed','','post2','','','2019-03-18 09:18:56','2019-03-18 09:18:56','',501,'http://wow.pebbled.io/schakraborty/softprodigy/1/wp-cont